      SUBROUTINE SETCFON(IFONT)
C
C   ROUTINE TO SET THE HALO STROKE TEXT FONT TO ONE OF THE FONTS SUPPORTED
C   BY CLICOM.
C
C    IFONT...CLICOM STROKE TEXT FONT NUMBER (1-9)
